The need for speed The Run competition across America.
Revision
Originally a race without a problem because of a series of errors stupid of people who have nothing to do with a morning routine at work.
This fills up to a certain extent the ambition of each but it achieves nothing if nobody wants to do something more.
The new Part subtitled The Run has produced great expectations before his exit.
He promised to take a new direction with the series of race Need for Speed already and a kind of game from the parties jouables that would not only with points.
We were curious how will be added the passages in which the main hero out of his car and does what he wants.
As already begun in the NFS series, the result is completely different than what we atttendait.
These are potentially games arcades race but the whole lower because of some unnecessary mistakes that already exist for several years.
They are not really mistakes but rather an expression of an incomprehensible laziness on the part of developers.
The adventure begins very well.
You are caught in the adventure whose main hero Jack has said problems and to address them is to participate in illegal racing across America.
You sit behind the wheel on the west coast in San Francisco and your mission is the first to arrive in New York.
The idea has some interesting points.
The itinerary is divided into ten steps and then in more than 50 races.
Which means that each race is on another route and the steps in different environments that differ quite well each other and are interesting.
The player does not have the sense that the game is something identical to it.
Some environments are also quite beautiful even if the technical level is the same kind of previous levels.
Finally it is not the end of the world.
But the driving through the desert, in landscapes of fall or in highly snow-covered mountains is very pleasant visually.
The tests are in addition from time to time with a non-standard element.
For example, in the desert you find yourself in a sandstorm that you decreases the visibility.
In the mountains and then you have to pay attention to what an avalanche do not fall over.
In addition to that the different races are well designed them one by one.
There is only a small number but that is enough.
There are moments you strive to exceed the number of opponents (as in a conventional running) and then you are against the clock (classic duel with the stopwatch) and then still awaits you another duel with an adversary.
From time to time you also have the police entering the game and trying to get the situation difficult.
The novelty outside the vehicle.
Rather, it is an interactive when most of the time Jack fled to someone and you have to help by slapping the right button at the right time.
Nothing complicated.
What is surprising is that there are moments of this type that what you want to be concrete (there are only three).
The result is this because this is not likely to hinder, in the context described above, in the elements that enhances the game.
The model of conduct is in the tradition of previous games.
Which means that currently there is nothing extraordinary but we cannot say that this is negative.
With regard to the realistic simulation you go see elsewhere.
But although there are better in the conccurrence the model of conduct goes very well with the type of design.
So everything is ok.
The problems start to appear after a period of time.
Has the diffférence model of conduct, that of collisions is not yet ready.
We do not expect this game a complicated and collisions, but when you did not, in a collision with any object, the slightest idea of how well your car, this is not completely good.
During the overruns tight you touch each other sometimes slightly but otherwise your car share in acrobatics mad.
Or is found.
Through the system, this is not really a problem but that you really riles.
The recovery is so that when you phut or you are out onto the stage the game you back at the time of the last point on the route.
But you have only 5 reboots.
When you have used the 5 reboots you have to start the game from the beginning.
It is therefore more a tool, in the event that something is not right, that old adage on which you can really count.
Sometimes the reboots do not help and we must find the solution in remémorrant memory piece of the route in question.
The central fault of this game is that the same actions are in the same places.
For example, there are some turns that we must move from a certain way otherwise it does not.
Otherwise you meet on a given location of vehicles "civilian" always in the same configuration that you have come first, fifth, 5 seconds ahead or a minute late.
The angry this are the situations when you see the adversary move easily between two cars coming in the opposite direction and when you arrive, you, you need to be set aside and the conturner or brake.
It is equal if you go out to him because it is "calculated" in such a way that for the given situation it is always close to your nose.
Opponents also have other benefits.
During the period of the game, you, you arrive in some places, again regardless of the time, and you still have the same opponent in front of you in the same place.
This is the thing most at the end when driving on a bridge in the opposite direction.
The enemy must at all costs to you.
When it passes you you obstructs the view of other vehicles in the opposite direction and you enter into a number of times.
It is understandable that the purpose of this game is to do something exciting and full of adrédaline, but it is clear that bored quickly.
And it is a pity because through a model of conduct simple the game is interesting and areas with both action that you do not have time to follow everything that happens.
And it is equal if it is because of the concept of 50 unique routes, the order of the races is such that there is no chance of being bored or something else.
The original idea is the change in car during the races.
You must pay attention to the fuel pumps on the routes because you can change cars but most of the time that you will suffice.
The cars are divided into three categories.
The sports cars are ideal for cities, the big-engined American for highways straight and the super sports cars to exotic trappings on the pipes very technical for example, on roads in lace in the mountains.
And the method of challenges, which are racing in particular places that you know of adventure, goes very well with the main plan of history.
You receive not only medals but also experience points to be added to your profile that is common to the challenges and adventure.
When you have reached the highest level of driver, different objects are beginning to unlock:
It connects with the on-line function Autolog which among other compares your results with those of other players and you provide other functions in the community.
One of the most difficult to understand is the situation of the last race of the adventure.
You arrive with your car in the tunnel subway (it looks like) where you drive in the dark on tracks (it looks like).
Your speedometer tells you between 150 and 200 km / hour (a priori) and behind you is a subway train that sends you the car directly to scrap metal.
Has the drafting we had a discussion for a few days to determine whether someone has actually thought at the time of the creation of this game or if the authors take us for fools.
The technical part of the game is not extra, but the visual part is generally pleasant and in some cases really cool.
Which hampers is that in more extreme situations, imaging is not the level and in some cases.
This concerns especially accidents with a large number of participants when a fluid does you no good.
The audio portion is good and the runway is choice.
In order to please the more and more particularly the young audience a new soundtrack was created in the style "I mix," but it can be expected that, and the game for music.
General impression of Need for Speed: The Run is really confused.
If the game had not these stupid mistakes we could say without fear that this is the best production of NTS in recent years.
But this game gives the impression of not being finished.
The amusement is really well but prepare you to ensure that the mistakes you type in the eye with the force of a reflector aerodrome.
The Students velvet in concert with the choir of the Charles University
The festival Festa Academica proposes for the third time of festivities that link the International Day student with the anniversary of the Velvet Revolution with a musical.
During the festival occur 20 choirs graduate schools and classes.
The highlight of the festival is composed of two concerts orgnisés on 17 November.
"Charles University has an important part in this festival."
"Among the choirs there is the Choir of the Faculty of Pedagogy and Humanities, in the festival seat President Vaclav Hampl," says the head of the organizing team Jakub Calou.
The highlight of the festival is the concert by the Choir of secondary schools and secondary classes held with free entry on 17 November from 14 hours on the space before the National Technical Library to Dejvice.
The program the composition of the well-known jazz Czech Karel Ruzicka, Celebration Jazz mass.
In the evening the concert "Students Velvet" in the premises of the House to national Vinohrady in which the chorus of high schools as well as that of the Charles University.
The Festa Academica aims not only to celebrate with dignity the International Day of students and the 22th anniversary of the Velvet Revolution, but also to present to the public a music choir at the highest level and develop the creative cooperation of young people.
The main organiser is the Union of the Czech world in cooperation with the Jan Kepler.
Any action is placed under the aegis of Bohuslav Svoboda, Mayor of Prague and Vaclav Hampl, Rector of the Charles University.
The festival takes place from 16 to 20 November in Prague and Pardubice.
The programme proposes addition concerts, meetings msicales happening, a student and other activities.
Interested parties will find all the information on the Internet pages of www.festaacademica.cz.
vicenova, Ambassador to the European Union:
The Czechs behave as négativistes and Eurosceptics
"The Treaty of Lisbon has radically deleted the balance between the institutions'
"I did not expect such a war as hard."
"It will last 5.6 years before the situation is calm and that all players get used to their new role," is how Miléna Vicenova began her presentation at the Faculty of Law Ambassador Czech near the European Union.
When she was able to describe the various organs of the EU and their relations so understandable and visible, to the point that a large number of speakers of the Faculty of Law of the Charles University could envy, it has shown how it takes its motto "understandable and openly about Europe" very seriously.
Madam Vicenova paid tribute to the work of Herman Van Rompuye, the new permanent President of the European Council.
"From the beginning echoed the criticism that it is bland, that this is a desk, that there can rempplir no mission and I must say that it has knocked the wind out of everyone because it takes its role to perfection."
"This is a man who listens to 27 Member States, communicate with them and has a clear vision of the direction of Europe."
She explained the new position of the High Representative for Foreign Affairs and Defence Policy in the context of an answer to the question: "Who is that the European Union?" "What do I call telephone number?," so as an important step towards the uniqueness and greater readability of the policy of the Union in the face of the statements, such as China or India.
Nobody wants to ban our syrecky (cheese cooked who feel very strong) 
Madam Vicenova also mentioned the agenda that has lived, lives and will live in a time near the European Council.
She described the Czech Presidency of two years ago of succeeding.
The Czech have solved the financial crisis, the gas crisis or have organized a summit for a Partnership Oriental.
She described the fall of the Government of very negative and has damaged the image of the Czech Republic.
The Czech representation to the EU is currently very busy.
In the words of the Ambassador, Madam "activity reached its high" not only for the Presidency but also for the financial crisis that continues to resolve even now.
There must also approve the new budget septimal of the Union which becomes very complicated because of the current economic situation.
As it would appear that the budget will be thin and economies, which industry will be the priority, which countries will be helped the most, the least, everything is to be resolved in the context of future negotiations.
Madam Ambassador recalled the slogans with which she arrived in Brussels "For an Europe understandable."
"I really don't like the foreign words, abbreviations, jargon that nobody understands.
As the citizen must understand that it is true that nobody in Brussels of gherkins or twisted, bananas, large or that nobody has prohibited syrecky. "
It wants to use the environment of the EU and see more of Czechs in the European institutions.
A multi-speed Europe awaits us
According to the Ambassador the Czechs have a reputation for being Eurosceptic and people who see the things that in their negative aspect that positively.
In addition it is sorry to see such a small Czech representation in the European institutions.
The fault is the result of several factors, such as the timidity of our candidates, their inability to write a letter of motivation and low support of the Czech part.
A Czech Presidency to success she then underlined the strength and the cooperation of the Visegrad.
"Believe me, when I come to the Poles, the Magyar, the Slovak, English said:" Hey, what you do, that there is still the Visegrad? "And it is not at all happy."
According to Ms. Vicenova, in the near future new rules hard fiscal policy facing the Member States.
This is the concept of a two-speed Europe, if not at different speeds, which is rather than a "new European Federation."
"We have countries in the euro area and other outside the area."
"We have the Schengen area, we also have the institute of enhanced cooperation."
First it was said that cooperation among the countries that do or do not want to remain in their corner. "
"There will be a lot of institutes of this type and there will be an Europe really two-speed" Madam, expects Vicenova.
From this point of view it also appreciated the mission of the Czech Republic and Herman Van Rompuye to determine the bases in which all the themes that have an impact on the EU must be discussed between all the members of the EU and not just the policy of the eurozone.
History of a mark:
The innovative IBM begins the second century of its existence
If someone had to seek the word which is as close to the IBM strategy, the nearest would be "the long term."
For a wide public IBM is the symbol of the technological revolution, is a firm perceived as very current and yet since its creation it took a hundred years.
The basis of this long-term strategy has been laid by the first head of the firm, the visionary Thomas J. Watson Sr.
He left the slogan that a large number of global problems can be solved if people are willing to think.
Its slogan "PENSE"! "Became the footprint around which will develop the life of a future giant (and also the title of the internal magazine that IBM began publishing in 1935).
It was the basis of the culture of the veritable developed by Watson.
IBM for us means thinking long-term continuous movements led to the future.
IBM has survived a hundred years thanks to the fact that she always remained true to its core values and yet has not been afraid to change all other around it.
This has allowed us during our first century of technology, business and society.
We hope that in the second century we will achieve even more "has reported for the anniversary the current Director of the firm Samuel J. Palmisano.
A system well prepared
Watson, in the thirties, began to take care of its employees as Bata in the Czech Republic - the people of IBM were the only one of the first American to have employees paid vacations, employer-paid insurance a more uniform of Employee elegant and a well developed system of rewards for inventors and the commmerciaux.
In the same way IBM has a system of relationships with the client well developed.
The company was brilliant early in the discovery of talents- as one of the first firms to abolish any form of discrimination and could have the choice.
The current plan is completely in the spirit of the anti-discrimination strategy because this will be a Rometty women- Virginia - which should replace Palmisano at the head of IBM.
It is working with IBM for thirty years and currently holds the position of Head of Sales, Marketing and Strategy.
IBM in recent years is what is known as the jamy, brain- storming online from what are many future strategies and innovations.
It is not surprising that he had a lot of ideas - in the firm nearly 500000 people work.
An institution with a good name
It is the internal and external image of the company that provide a secure position in the areas of business.
"Since the beginning IBM had a concept of institution rather than a firm technology," said Rosabeth Moss Kanter, Professor of Economics at the Harvard School of Economics and author of the book on IBM.
"IBM is not a firm Technology Policy but a firm that helps solve problems of the world of business using its technology," added Geogre Consulting firm Colony of Forrester Research.
As the firm itself there is a difference between enter the market and create this market.
IBM - or the "Great Blue," as it is known in the United States with regard to its slogan- in a hundred years it has grown into one of the largest global firms.
This is obviously the most versatile technology firm - it develops software, hardwares, infrastructure, accommodation, services of Council at the level of the products of the server to nanotechnology.
It has many patents of all technology firms American and five of its employees received a Nobel Prize.
Among his discoveries is for example, the distributor of tickets, the payment card, the financial swap, the bar code or the diskette.
IBM found itself this year with $220 billion in the second largest technology firm by market capitalization (the first is Apple), when for the first time it exceeded in 1996 Microsoft.
Overview in advance
Not all innovations and manufacturing who have had the preference of the client and the time - IBM for example, has failed the bet on an operational system own OS / 2, the service Prodige online or of the IBM computer PCjr:
"From the moment that your business is built on the movement in advance you cannot émotionellement remain fixated on the past," noted Samuel J. Palmisano.
For that IBM does not have a problem to build its bases on many platforms and when they do not work she is headed.
Unlike for example, of conccurent Microsoft that at the base is and remains under the Windows operating system.
A technology perspective
In the IBM, services, which are trained to a fifth by the software and hardwares, have a prominent place.
Yet in 1990 it was with more than the motié participation the highest representative of hardware.
From the year 2000 IBM sold assets to low performance for $15 billion, during cettre period it has invested $58 billion in the purchase of technologies.
It continues in investments and even from 2008, when for the first time it has surpassed the new financial crisis.
IBM negotiates according to the requirements of its first head Thomas J. Watson, who during the great economic crisis has also increased its volume of investments.
Now it appears that IBM is the current crisis without interference?
The stock price IBM has progessé from 2008 in rocket by 120 percent, the net profit of the firm continues to grow.
The company's logo IBM is to change but not its values.
It is for this that this giant flexible control other crises.
History of IBM: A from slices of cheese to flights in the cosmos.
The International Business Machines (IBM) was born in New York one hundred years ago; she had initially the complicated name of Computing Tabulating Recording Corporation.
She took the name IBM in 1924 - initially it was a mark used by a branch of a firm in Canada and South America.
The basis of the future IBM was the merger of four firms whose history is linked to 80 of the nineteenth century.
They had technologies such as the old "clocking," clocks that recorded the arrival and departure of employees.
The architect of the new company was Ranlett Charles Flint that until 1930 the Supervisory Board of society.
Flint hired the head of a rival firm Thomas J. Watson to help lead the company.
The leader of the then shadow the founder of the business - it is on the ideas of Watson that are up to now the identity and culture of the society.
Watson led the firm kusqu" in 1952.
IBM, as the name suggests, began with the production of all machinery possible for business and trade - of cheese slicers and meat until the cash registers.
In the first four years during which Watson led, the turnover is multiplied up to $9 million and began the expansion of the firm in all parts of the world.
Watson was for the firm if irreplaceable that after 40 years of leadership is the son who took the Chair of Director, Thomas Watson Junior.
Under his leadership IBM began the development of artificial intelligence and developed the first language of programming.
In the 60 s people and computers IBM NASA has helped guide the flights in the cosmos - on Mercury, Saturn and in 1969 the flight on the Moon.
Meanwhile in 1964 IBM developed the first family computer - the IBM System / 360.
The PC classic which determined the standard computer at the time with the name of IBM 5150 arrived on the market in 1981.
Twenty years later IBM sells its manufactures computers to the Chinese company Lenovo, but bought the company Consulting Pricewaterhouse Coopers and began to take on board and services with high added value.
The strategy that succeeds in IBM in the last three years - is the concept Smarter Planet "a planet smarter."
Its objective is the smart use of technology in areas such as for example, the transport and management of cities.
With regard to the area of trade IBM has developed a short time ago a platform "Smarter Commerce" that helps marketers to manage the business cycle.
IBM has a strong history also on our territory.
She set up its branch in Czechoslovakia in 1932 when first countries of Central and Eastern Europe.
Today, in addition to IBM RT, there is also the strategic centre for outsourcing of Brno.
The Central for the Central and Eastern European seat in Prague and there is also the team's research and development that is responsible for the recognition of the floor.
