Now I read "Crime and Punishment," this is a book of universal literature that we should read all; and now I read the book of Irene Nemirovski, a Russian, a very beautiful book called "The love of the blood." "
This response was not the first because of the term "culturaliser" and secondly for not explain specifically how each book cited the had marked.
But at the end of the ceremony Melina said that she felt quiet and happy with the outcome "universe and wise, it is what has to happen.
And for all the world, see you a little, "The Little Prince" is a great book "
